  "title": "Beauty and Wellness Supervisor",
  "description": "<ul><li>Oversee daily operations of the beauty and wellness outlet to ensure smooth and efficient workflow.</li></ul><ul><li>Supervise, coach, and motivate therapists, beauticians, and consultants to maintain high service standards.</li></ul><ul><li>Plan staff schedules, manage manpower deployment, and ensure adequate coverage at all times.</li></ul><ul><li>Monitor staff performance, productivity, and customer service quality.</li></ul><ul><li>Handle customer feedback, complaints, and service recovery in a professional and timely manner.</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure strict compliance with hygiene, safety, and health regulations.</li></ul><ul><li>Conduct regular team briefings and on-the-job training to upgrade staff skills and knowledge.</li></ul><ul><li>Support sales targets by promoting treatment packages, memberships, and retail products.</li></ul><ul><li>Track daily sales performance and prepare basic operational and sales reports.</li></ul><ul><li>Manage inventory levels, place purchase orders, and coordinate with suppliers and vendors.</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure proper maintenance of equipment and treatment rooms.</li></ul><ul><li>Implement and monitor standard operating procedures (SOPs) across all service areas.</li></ul><ul><li>Assist management in developing service promotions and customer retention programs.</li></ul><ul><li>Maintain high standards of staff grooming, professionalism, and workplace conduct.</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure accurate appointment scheduling and effective use of booking systems.</li></ul>",
